    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arch Legends 是一款经典的第三人称即时战斗角色扮演游戏！强大的存在正在涌现，埃弗雷斯卡王国指望你来消灭黑暗势力。你有能力恢复世界秩序吗？召唤盟友或在玩家之间进行全球黑市交易，帮助恢复王国的和平与秩序！ Arch Legends 将经典 RPG 传统与其他创新机制相结合，创造出无与伦比的 RPG 体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该游戏将带来数次冒险，就好像游戏大师讲述经典的角色扮演战役一样，玩家将从新内容中受益，除此之外，它还将提供完全免费的季票。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>没有微交易！没有现金店！</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗非常激烈且具有策略性，任何错误都可能让你输掉比赛。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/c37d751fa7192654eaf9b359c3f1113d.poster.avif?t=1731027657\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/c37d751fa7192654eaf9b359c3f1113d.webm?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/c37d751fa7192654eaf9b359c3f1113d.mp4?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩家可以选择多种职业和能力，每种职业和能力都有自己的优点和缺点！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/26762365c533b990af55e27ed83007e3.poster.avif?t=1731027657\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/26762365c533b990af55e27ed83007e3.webm?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/26762365c533b990af55e27ed83007e3.mp4?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩家可以召唤盟友来帮助他们面对更大的挑战并获得丰厚的奖励！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/fb3ad49dc7e3f0cbdf3dfe650c4387d5.poster.avif?t=1731027657\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/fb3ad49dc7e3f0cbdf3dfe650c4387d5.webm?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/fb3ad49dc7e3f0cbdf3dfe650c4387d5.mp4?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩家可以加入公会并执行特殊任务，进化并获得独特的奖励来兑换特殊物品！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/ada1da6a7a817fdec98ea236780cf730.poster.avif?t=1731027657\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/ada1da6a7a817fdec98ea236780cf730.webm?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131770/extras/ada1da6a7a817fdec98ea236780cf730.mp4?t=1731027657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
